{"info": {"author": "Marcus McCurdy", "author_email": "marcus.mccurdy@gmail.com", "bugtrack_url": null, "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Environment :: Web Environment", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP :: Dynamic Content", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules"], "description": "Flask-Mandrill\n==============\n\nA Flask Extension to remove some of the boiler plate encountered when\nsending emails with `Mandrill <http://www.mandrill.com/>`_\n\nInstallation\n````````````\n\n.. code:: bash\n\n    $ pip install flask-mandrill\n\n\nUsage\n`````\n\n.. code:: python\n\n        from flask import Flask\n        from flask.ext.mandrill import Mandrill\n\n        app = Flask(__name__)\n        app.config['MANDRILL_API_KEY'] = 'your api key'\n        mandrill = Mandrill(app)\n        mandrill.send_email(\n            from_email='someone@yourdomain.com',\n            to=[{'email': 'someoneelse@someotherdomain.com'}],\n            text='Hello World'\n        )\n\n\n.. :changelog:\n\nRelease History\n---------------\n\n\n0.2 (2015-01-15)\n++++++++++++++++\n\n- Adds support for sending template emails.\n\n0.1.1 (2013-10-25)\n++++++++++++++++++\n\n- Added config option MANDRILL_DEFAULT_FROM.\n\n0.1.0 (2012-10-25)\n++++++++++++++++++\n\n- First release.", "description_content_type": null, "docs_url": null, "download_url": "UNKNOWN", "downloads": {"last_day": -1, "last_month": -1, "last_week": -1}, "home_page": "http://github.com/volker48/flask-mandrill", "keywords": null, "license": "MIT", "maintainer": null, "maintainer_email": null, "name": "Flask-Mandrill", "package_url": "https://pypi.org/project/Flask-Mandrill/", "platform": "any", "project_url": "https://pypi.org/project/Flask-Mandrill/", "project_urls": {"Download": "UNKNOWN", "Homepage": "http://github.com/volker48/flask-mandrill"}, "release_url": "https://pypi.org/project/Flask-Mandrill/0.3/", "requires_dist": null, "requires_python": null, "summary": "Adds Mandrill support to Flask applications", "version": "0.3", "yanked": false, "html_description": "<div class=\"project-description\">\n            <p>A Flask Extension to remove some of the boiler plate encountered when\nsending emails with <a href=\"http://www.mandrill.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mandrill</a></p>\n<div id=\"installation\">\n<h2>Installation</h2>\n<pre>$ pip install flask-mandrill\n</pre>\n</div>\n<div id=\"usage\">\n<h2>Usage</h2>\n<pre><span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">flask</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Flask</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">from</span> <span class=\"nn\">flask.ext.mandrill</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span> <span class=\"n\">Mandrill</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">app</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Flask</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"vm\">__name__</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">app</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"s1\">'MANDRILL_API_KEY'</span><span class=\"p\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"s1\">'your api key'</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mandrill</span> <span class=\"o\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">Mandrill</span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">app</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">mandrill</span><span class=\"o\">.</span><span class=\"n\">send_email</span><span class=\"p\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">from_email</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'someone@yourdomain.com'</span><span class=\"p\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"p\">[{</span><span class=\"s1\">'email'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"s1\">'someoneelse@someotherdomain.com'</span><span class=\"p\">}],</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">text</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s1\">'Hello World'</span>\n<span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</pre>\n<div id=\"release-history\">\n<h3>Release History</h3>\n<div id=\"id1\">\n<h4>0.2 (2015-01-15)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Adds support for sending template emails.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id2\">\n<h4>0.1.1 (2013-10-25)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Added config option MANDRILL_DEFAULT_FROM.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"id3\">\n<h4>0.1.0 (2012-10-25)</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First release.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n          </div>"}, "last_serial": 2196027, "releases": {"0.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "28366ff839b6f6374e2bf02a08e28210", "sha256": "43cb80180725ddb1f144aa03c6e307be9d0303eda39f2f7bc3ae031f0ae90198"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "Flask-Mandrill-0.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "28366ff839b6f6374e2bf02a08e28210", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 1798, "upload_time": "2013-10-25T15:27:44", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2013-10-25T15:27:44.625256Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/51/bb/7392e6b454dafec871173d807c011fd7bb003d73b69316a1e3185759b45e/Flask-Mandrill-0.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.1.1": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "2f9121e4b249681a7b040de261edc24e", "sha256": "32a2af91f7d69bed225aef1ca48d104e9158dfd44720db4365e613c9fd40dc79"}, "downloads": -1, "filename": "Flask-Mandrill-0.1.1.tar.gz", "has_sig": false, "md5_digest": "2f9121e4b249681a7b040de261edc24e", "packagetype": "sdist", "python_version": "source", "requires_python": null, "size": 2403, "upload_time": "2013-10-25T18:04:10", "upload_time_iso_8601": "2013-10-25T18:04:10.357438Z", "url": "https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/2c/b4/61ce11db77790f5c7de9e5b44c1faf157551a97103131212ce7fda1a724c/Flask-Mandrill-0.1.1.tar.gz", "yanked": false}], "0.2": [{"comment_text": "", "digests": {"md5": "e6870f0db8a77289199876b520aaa1a4", "sha256": "46ee974790cdc29bd150f9a1abf6f599ca3f634b5fc5e9fe7cf399c1adfdcdab"}, "downloads": 